                "invention-title": [
                    "Solar-driven thermoelectric power generation coupling water electrolysis hydrogen production device",
                    "一种太阳能驱动温差发电耦合电解水制氢装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of clean energy development, and particularly relates to a solar-driven thermoelectric power generation coupling water electrolysis hydrogen production device. The solar thermoelectric generator is designed and constructed by utilizing a light-heat conversion material and the like, and the solar thermoelectric generator and the electrolytic bath are connected in series and integrated, so that the multi-energy fusion type integrated device of the sunlight-driven thermoelectric power generation coupled electrolytic bath is obtained. According to the invention, the light-heat conversion characteristic and the heat-electricity conversion characteristic of the solar thermoelectric generator are utilized to realize efficient conversion from solar heat energy to electric energy, and the converted electric energy is further used for electrolyzing water to prepare hydrogen; therefore, comprehensive development and utilization of a multi-energy fusion type clean energy technology system for converting solar energy into heat energy, converting heat energy into electric energy, converting electric energy into hydrogen energy and the like are realized. The device provided by the invention not only solves the problems of electric energy output, storage and utilization in solar thermoelectric power generation, but also can convert solar energy into hydrogen energy with high energy density."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于清洁能源开发技术领域，具体涉及一种太阳能驱动温差发电耦合电解水制氢装置。本发明利用光‑热转化材料等设计和构筑出太阳能温差发电器，并将太阳能温差发电器和电解槽串联集成，得到太阳光驱动温差发电耦合电解槽的多能融合型集成装置。本发明利用太阳能温差发电器的光‑热转化特性和热‑电转化特性，实现太阳热能向电能的高效转化，进一步将转化的电能用于电解水制取氢气，继而实现太阳能向热能转化、热能向电能转化以及电能向氢能转化等多能融合型清洁能源技术体系的综合开发利用。本发明提供的装置不仅解决了太阳能温差发电中电能输出及存储利用的问题，而且能够将太阳能转化为高能量密度的氢能。"
                }
            ]
